    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted for the stated decision purpose.",
